Istvn Kovcs (born 1950 in Ndudvar) is a Hungarian wrestler. He was born in Ndudvar in Hajd-Bihar County. He was Olympic bronze medalist in Freestyle wrestling in 1980. He won a gold medal at the 1979 World Wrestling Championships.[1] 
